title: Madoff Client List, World
name: Madoff Client List, World
description: This dataset was made from a document from the Wall Street Journal which listed the clients of Madoff (labeled exhibit A). The US locations were geocoded to the zipcode using batch geocoded and aggregated. The international clients were geocoded to the city, except for small countries and islands such as Andorra or St Lucia. These were also geocoded using batch geocode and are aggrigated. Nearly 200 or the 11,953 clients were not geocodeable.
